OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness across
OL,6,Fthe south but generally a cloudy
OL,7,Fmorning with outbreaks of rain, most
OL,8,Fpersistent and occasionally heavy
OL,9,Facross Argyll. The cloud and rain edge
OL,10,Fnorth this afternoon with most places
OL,11,Fbecoming dry with some sunny spells
OL,12,Fdeveloping.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,15,Fsunny spells then long clear spells
OL,16,Fovernight. Cloud increases towards
OL,17,Fdawn with perhaps a little rain for
OL,18,FKintyre and the Isles later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
