OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome early brightness for
OL,6,FAyrshire and Lanarkshire, otherwise a
OL,7,Fmostly cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain, occasionally heavy especially
OL,9,Facross Argyll. The rain turns more
OL,10,Fshowery in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,14,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,15,FMainly dry and bright Monday with
OL,16,Fsunny spells, but cloudier Tuesday
OL,17,Fwith occasionally heavy rain or
OL,18,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
